data.description: Great Tri-Level Home with Huge Backyard! Newer Luxury Plank Vinyl Flooring throughout main level and lower level. The main level has large windows allowing natural light to pour in. The eat in kitchen flows into to the huge backyard with wood deck, mature trees, and 2 included storage sheds.  The garage is just off the kitchen for easy access. The upper level boasts the large primary bedroom, full bathroom and another good size bedroom with walk in closet. The lower level has a 2nd living room, the 3rd bedroom, 1/2 bathroom, laundry (washer and dryer included!) and storage in the crawl space. Whole house water filtration system is included with the house. Security System is in place and will just need new membership. New roof in 2018! Convenient access to neighborhood park, schools, Academy Blvd with tons of restaurants and stores, Peterson Air Force Base, Ft Carson and I-25.
